<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package>
	<metadata>
    <id>DataverseToPowerBI.XrmToolBox</id>
    <version>1.2026.5.155</version>
    <title>Dataverse to Power BI Semantic Model</title>
    <authors>Scott Sewell</authors>
    <owners>mScottSewell</owners>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <license type="expression">MIT</license>
    <description>Extract Dataverse metadata and generate Power BI TMDL/PBIP semantic models with automatic table relationships, calendar tables, and incremental change detection.</description>
    <summary>XrmToolBox plugin for generating Power BI semantic models from Dataverse metadata</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
v1.2026.5.154 - Advanced table selection release

New in this release:
- Add Tables to Model dialog: include any Dataverse table in the Power BI semantic model, even if it is not reachable through the standard lookup-chain discovery.
  - Full-environment table browser filtered to show only tables not already in the star schema.
  - Instant search/filter by display name or logical name.
  - Manual relationship builder lets you define column-level joins between any two tables (source table/column → target table/column, active/inactive, referential integrity).
  - Edit support: re-opening the wizard restores previously configured additional tables and relationships.
  - Live count badge in the wizard shows the number of additional tables and relationships pending.
- Additional tables and manually-defined relationships are persisted to the semantic model configuration and fully restored on reload.
- Lookup columns required by manually-defined relationships are automatically included in the model (same enforcement as auto-discovered relationships).

Previous highlights (v1.2026.5.146):
- Display-name renaming executes in Power Query via Table.RenameColumns instead of SQL AS aliases.
- SQL projections remain stable technical/logical names.
- Semantic model save/copy flows persist rename setting, storage mode, and choice numeric defaults consistently.

Full details: CHANGELOG.md
    </releaseNotes>
    <tags>XrmToolBox PowerBI Dataverse TMDL PBIP SemanticModel</tags>
